title: She-Hulk (2022-2023) #11
description: New arc! Great jumping on point! A new villain starts a thieving spree through New York City and ends up face-to-green-face with Jennifer Walters, the Sensational She-Hulk! Also, have you noticed that this is LGY #174? You'd almost think something very special is coming!
author: Rainbow Rowell
